` — Binary entry point with flags and graceful shutdown\n270: - [ ] `cmd/workload-manager/main.go` — Binary entry point with flags and graceful shutdown\n271: - [ ] `cmd/picod/main.go` — Binary entry point with flags and graceful shutdown\n272: - [ ] `pkg/common/signal` — Shared signal handling package\n273: - [ ] `pkg/common/version` — Shared version package\n274: - [ ] All 4 binaries compile successfully\n275: - [ ] All 4 binaries print help with `--help`\n276: - [ ] All 4 binaries handle SIGINT/SIGTERM gracefully\n277: \n278: ---\n279: \n280: ## References\n281: \n282: - [deployment/design.md](/deployment/design.md) — Build targets and Docker image specs\n283: - [AR-009/delta-spec.md](/changes/AR-009/delta-spec.md) — Router flags specification\n284: - [AR-007/delta-spec.md](/changes/AR-007/delta-spec.md) — Workload manager controller spec\n285: - [code-execution/spec.md](/code-execution/spec.md) — Picod server spec\n286: - [idle-cleanup/spec.md](/idle-cleanup/spec.md) — Agentd binary spec\n\n(End of file - total 286 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-019 — CLI 二进制入口 (4 binaries)\n\n> **Module:** `cmd`  \n> **Language:** Go  \n> **Size:** M  \n> **Stage:** ST-3 (Design) Completed → ST-4 (Implementation)  \n> **Base Spec:** project.md, deployment/design.md\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nAR-019 implements the CLI binary entry points for the 4 core AgentCube components:\n1. **agentd** - Idle cleanup controller binary\n2. **router** - Session routing proxy binary  \n3. **workload-manager** - Sandbox orchestration binary\n4. **picod** - Sandbox daemon binary\n\nEach binary SHALL parse CLI flags, initialize configuration, wire dependencies, start the respective service, and handle graceful shutdown via OS signals.\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-019/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775884179073,"end":1775884179098}}}}
